"The customer service was fantastic and very helpful."
"This movie is not bad at all, I actually enjoyed it quite a bit."
"The new update has greatly improved performance and fixed many bugs 👍"
"Despite a few minor issues, I'm very satisfied with my purchase 😊"

Negative Examples:
